---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="legal">
    <div class="top">
      <header>
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="meta">Effective date: November 4, 2025</div>
      </header>
      <nav aria-label="On this page">
        <ul>
          <li><a href="#overview">1. Overview</a></li>
          <li><a href="#collect">2. Information We Collect</a></li>
          <li><a href="#third-parties">3. Third-Party Services</a></li>
          <li><a href="#sharing">4. Data Sharing</a></li>
          <li><a href="#cookies">5. Cookies</a></li>
          <li><a href="#security">6. Security</a></li>
          <li><a href="#international">7. International Use</a></li>
          <li><a href="#changes">8. Changes</a></li>
          <li><a href="#contact">9. Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <p>This policy explains how <strong>New Dashboard</strong> ("we", "our", "us") handles information.</p>

    <h2 id="overview">1. Overview</h2>
    <p>We do <strong>not</strong> collect or store personal or financial data. The app is free and web-only.</p>

    <h2 id="collect">2. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may process limited technical data (e.g., IP address, device/browser details, and basic usage logs) to operate and secure the app, troubleshoot, and improve performance.</p>

    <h2 id="third-parties">3. Use of Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google</strong> (e.g., analytics/performance tooling)</li>
      <li><strong>Supabase</strong> (hosting/database platform)</li>
    </ul>
    <p>These vendors may temporarily process technical data to provide their services. We do not link this data to identified individuals.</p>

    <h2 id="sharing">4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, rent, or share data with third parties beyond the service providers named above.</p>

    <h2 id="cookies">5. Cookies and Local Storage</h2>
    <p>We may use cookies or local storage for session state and basic functionality. You can block cookies in your browser; some features may not work as intended.</p>

    <h2 id="security">6. Security</h2>
    <p>We use reasonable technical and organizational measures appropriate to the data we handle. No system is perfectly secure.</p>

    <h2 id="international">7. International Use</h2>
    <p>Services are operated from Canada. By using the app, you consent to processing in Canada under Canadian law, which may differ from your jurisdiction.</p>

    <h2 id="changes">8. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this policy. The effective date will reflect the latest version.</p>

    <h2 id="contact">9. Contact</h2>
    <address>
      <div><strong>New Computer Entertainment Inc.</strong></div>
      <div>83 Walnut Ave, Toronto, ON M5V 2S1, Canada</div>
      <div>Email: <a href="mailto:email@newsystems.ca">email@newsystems.ca</a></div>
    </address>

    <hr />
    <p class="muted">Company: New Computer Entertainment Inc. — App: New Dashboard</p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .legal {
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .top {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: 12px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .meta {
    margin: 8px 0 16px;
    font-size: var(--font-size-small);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .legal nav ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    gap: 6px;
  }

  .legal nav a {
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .legal nav a::after {
    content: none;
  }

  .legal nav a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  address {
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .muted {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  h2 {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-lg);
  }
</style>
